TextArea((24.0, 557.0), (154.0, 211.0)) {'type': 'CAMERON'}
  [
    u'DAVID CAMERON: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'CAMERON'}
    u"You're reminding me of Gordon last week. It's like another replay. The fact is, every year, you " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'need to talk with the health authorities, the housing authorities, the education authorities, and ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'business, and set a cap to achieve a very big reduction in overall immigration levels. That can ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"be done, we've done it in our past, we can do it again in our future. What's required is political " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"will from a party that's prepared to make the difference.  " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((24.0, 563.0), (223.0, 314.0)) {'type': 'CLEGG'}
  [
    u'NICK CLEGG: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'CLEGG'}
    u"David Cameron, you are... Let me get this straight, I genuinely want to understand, you're " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"proposing a cap but you don't know what the cap would be. You're proposing to give people an " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"assurance that we're going to count people in and count people out, but you don't know how " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"many people. All I'm saying on the immigration debate, it's difficult, none of us have got perfect " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"answers. But let's at least not pretend that you can put forward these ideas which have got no " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"substance, haven't been thought through. At least the kind of ideas I've been putting through " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'are trying to deal with a really, really difficult issue which has been brushed under the carpet ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'for too long.  ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((24.0, 211.0), (326.0, 337.0)) {'type': 'INTERVIEWER'}
  [
